OL,3,C'Agony': Savannah Guthrie's first
OL,4,Cinterview since mother's disappearance
OL,6,FSpeaking with her longtime friend and
OL,7,Fcolleague Hoda Kotb, Guthrie said: "We
OL,8,Fare in agony, we are in agony. It is
OL,9,Funbearable."
OL,11,FShe revealed she wakes up "every
OL,12,Fnight" and thinks about the "terror"
OL,13,Fher mother went through.
OL,15,FNBC released a brief excerpt from the
OL,16,Finterview on Wednesday morning, ahead
OL,17,Fof airing an extended version in two
OL,18,Fparts on Thursday and Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
