OL,3,C'Agony': Savannah Guthrie's first
OL,4,Cinterview since mother's disappearance
OL,6,FAuthorities have been looking for
OL,7,FNancy Guthrie since she went missing
OL,8,Fon February 1.
OL,10,FDespite offering a $1 million reward
OL,11,Ffor information, there has been little
OL,12,Fmovement in the investigation.
OL,14,FFootage revealing a masked figure
OL,15,Foutside the home of Nancy Guthrie was
OL,16,Freleased, and alleged ransom notes
OL,17,Fwere reported, but no police suspect
OL,18,Fhas been identified.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
