OL,3,C'Agony': Savannah Guthrie's first
OL,4,Cinterview since mother's disappearance
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FGuthrie's family last weekend appealed
OL,12,Fto neighbours in Arizona to search
OL,13,Fback through their memories for
OL,14,Fanything they might have seen that
OL,15,Fcould help the investigation.
OL,17,F"No detail is too small," they said.
