OL,3,C'Agony': Savannah Guthrie's first
OL,4,Cinterview since mother's disappearance
OL,6,FIt is thought that Savannah Guthrie is
OL,7,Fpreparing to return to the Today show,
OL,8,Falthough the network has not announced
OL,9,Fa date.
OL,11,FAccording to ITV New's US partner CNN,
OL,12,F"a person close to the show said they
OL,13,Fanticipate Guthrie coming back to
OL,14,FStudio 1A sometime in April".
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
